WEBVTT

00:02.086 --> 00:03.495
Aliens killed my wife.

00:03.496 --> 00:05.315
It wasn't my hate that kept me going.

00:05.316 --> 00:06.595
It was my love...

00:06.596 --> 00:08.445
Previously on Falling Skies...

00:08.446 --> 00:09.645
Since I woke up with the spikes,

00:09.646 --> 00:11.176
I feel like... I'm drawn to you.

00:12.256 --> 00:13.505
Espheni power core,

00:13.506 --> 00:15.585
was never on Earth in the first place.

00:15.586 --> 00:19.236
It powers the entire Espheni war machine.

00:19.506 --> 00:21.226
We are gonna blow that son of bitch up.

00:21.716 --> 00:23.165
Who do you propose

00:23.166 --> 00:25.716
to pilot that flying saucer to the moon?

00:25.726 --> 00:26.246
Me.

00:26.247 --> 00:27.806
Let me be your weapon.

00:29.646 --> 00:30.976
Bye, Daddy.

00:34.136 --> 00:35.725
Tom always finds his way home.

00:35.726 --> 00:37.805
That overlord said that
there was a danger coming,

00:37.806 --> 00:39.055
and until he does...

00:39.056 --> 00:41.246
We have to finish what he started.

00:41.846 --> 00:44.256
We have to end this war.

00:45.256 --> 00:47.936
<i>Tom Mason. It's about time.</i>

00:49.000 --> 00:55.074
